casebody.data:
Wesley Eugene BROOKS, petitioner,
v.
MINNESOTA; and Wesley Eugene Brooks, petitioner,
v.
Minnesota. No. 12-478. Supreme Court of the United States April 22, 2013.

On petition for writ of certiorari to the Court of Appeals of Minnesota. Petition for writ of certiorari granted. Judgments vacated, and cases remanded to the Court of Appeals of Minnesota for further consideration in light of Missouri v. McNeely, 569 U.S. ----, 133 S.Ct. 1552, ---L.Ed.2d ---- (2013).
